*a)* What is the minimum coefficient of restitution of a _FIFA Approved_ soccer ball?

[`e_{min}=`] [_____]{"$emin"}

*b)* What is the maximum coefficient of restitution of a _FIFA Approved_ soccer ball?

[`e_{max}=`] [_____]{"$emax"} 

